TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed HttpRequestHeader extends System.Enum

summary.span: 用戶端要求中可能指定的 HTTP 標頭。

span.span: The HTTP headers that may be specified in a client request.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 各種不同的標頭的適當的內容所述在 HTTP/1.1 規格中，可在詳細資料[rfc2616](https://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616.html)。The appropriate contents of various headers are described in detail in the HTTP/1.1 specification, available at [rfc2616](https://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616.html).
